{# AOS-CX (ArubaOS-CX) uses "severity info" — NOT the Cisco IOS keyword
   "informational". Syslog severity keyword differs per platform:
     Cisco IOS/IOS-XE : logging trap informational
     Cisco IOS-XR     : logging ... severity info  (also "logging trap informational")
     AOS-CX (Aruba)   : logging ... severity info        <- here
     Arista EOS       : logging trap informational
     FortiOS          : config log syslogd filter / set severity information
     SonicWall        : GUI/REST API, no CLI template
   Sending "informational" to AOS-CX is rejected by the CLI. #}
logging {{ collector_ip }} severity info
logging on
